<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>마이페이지 - Photo Diary</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.10.5/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
</head>
<body class="bg-light">

<nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light bg-white shadow-sm mb-4">
    <div class="container">
        <a class="navbar-brand fw-bold text-primary" href="/">
            <i class="bi bi-camera-fill"></i> Photo Diary
        </a>
        <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3">
            <span class="text-muted small"><i class="bi bi-person"></i> {{name}}님</span>
            <form action="/mypage/logout" method="post" class="m-0">
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm">로그아웃</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
</nav>

<div class="container">
    <h5 class="fw-bold mb-4"><i class="bi bi-box-seam me-2"></i>내 주문 현황</h5>

    {{#orders}}
        <div class="card shadow-sm border-0 rounded-4 mb-3">
            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-2">
                    <span class="fw-bold text-dark">주문 #{{id}}</span>
                    <span class="badge rounded-pill {{statusColor}}">
                        {{#isPending}}접수 대기{{/isPending}}
                        {{#isProcessing}}처리 중{{/isProcessing}}
                        {{#isCompleted}}배송 완료{{/isCompleted}}
                        {{#isRejected}}반려{{/isRejected}}
                    </span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-muted small mb-1"><i class="bi bi-geo-alt"></i> {{shippingAddress}}</p>
                <p class="text-muted small mb-0"><i class="bi bi-calendar3"></i> {{formattedDate}}</p>

                {{^isRejected}}
                <div class="mt-3 d-flex gap-2 align-items-center">
                    <div class="progress flex-grow-1" style="height: 6px;">
                        {{#isPending}}
                            <div class="progress-bar bg-secondary" style="width: 33%"></div>
                        {{/isPending}}
                        {{#isProcessing}}
                            <div class="progress-bar bg-warning" style="width: 66%"></div>
                        {{/isProcessing}}
                        {{#isCompleted}}
                            <div class="progress-bar bg-success" style="width: 100%"></div>
                        {{/isCompleted}}
                    </div>
                    <span class="text-muted small" style="white-space: nowrap;">
                        {{#isPending}}1/3{{/isPending}}
                        {{#isProcessing}}2/3{{/isProcessing}}
                        {{#isCompleted}}3/3{{/isCompleted}}
                    </span>
                </div>
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-between mt-1" style="font-size: 0.7rem; color: #adb5bd;">
                    <span>접수 대기</span>
                    <span>처리 중</span>
                    <span>배송 중</span>
                </div>
                {{/isRejected}}
                {{#isRejected}}
                <div class="mt-3 text-danger small">
                    <i class="bi bi-x-circle"></i> 이 주문은 반려되었습니다.
                </div>
                {{/isRejected}}
            </div>
        </div>
    {{/orders}}

    {{^orders}}
        <div class="text-center py-5 text-muted">
            <i class="bi bi-inbox display-4 d-block mb-3"></i>
            <p>아직 주문 내역이 없어요.</p>
            <a href="/" class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-sm">다이어리 보러가기</a>
        </div>
    {{/orders}}

    <div class="mt-4 text-center pb-5">
        <a href="/" class="btn btn-link text-decoration-none text-secondary small">
            <i class="bi bi-arrow-left"></i> 메인 화면으로
        </a>
    </div>
</div>

<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
